				.main-descr--left
					h2.title FEATURED OFFER
					div
						h1 SOCIAL PANDAS
						.ye-line
						.net socialpandas.net
				.main-descr--right
					include ../parts/rating.pug
					a(href="offers.html#feedback" class="old-price__reviews") 999 reviews
					include ../parts/timer.pug
			.main-descr
				div
					.main-descr__descr
						| I'm speaking with myself, number one, because I have a very good brain and I've said a lot of things. Lorem Ipsum best not make any more threats to your website. It will be met with fire and fury like the world has never seen. I&rsquo;m the best thing that ever happened to placeholder text.
